description:
Finally you will be able to play the most interesting Pop It!
You will come across a very diverse heroes that you can go through and burst all the pimples.

Play Spider-Man, Batman, Baby Yoda, unicorn, avocado and other equally interesting characters! In any case, you can create your own Pop It. Color it as you like, put interesting seals. Unlock all the items from the game and compete on the leaderboard.

Advantages:

- Many different Pop It models;
- exciting levels;
- you can create your own Pop It;
- put the seals on the Pop it

MERGE BLOCK PUZZLE is a FREE and FUN puzzle game for all ages;
MERGE BLOCK PUZZLE is a good game to help you relax and train your brain;

How to play this puzzle game?
• Drag the number blocks to move them.
